*Readme file for run_analysis.R

*the scrip does NOT assume that data is already available in the current working directory
*the script downloads and unzips the data to whatever the current directory is
*subject and activity columns have been added as the last two columns of the data set
*variables have been renamed according to the recommended safe naming conventions at Coursera “Getting and cleaning Data” course: lowercase, no dash, no parenthesis. 
